# No ROC mentions

This website must **never** display **中華民國** or **Republic of China** anywhere — not in page copy, footers, CMS content, metadata, or UI labels.

## Rules

- Do not add, restore, or leave these terms in source files, Sanity schemas, seed data, or static HTML.
- When editing Chinese copy, rephrase around the reference (e.g. use 教育部, not 中華民國教育部).
- CMS strings are sanitized in `src/lib/zh-copy.ts` (`stripRocMentions`, `normalizeZhCopy`); extend those helpers if new entry points appear.
- Font attributions must not cite 中華民國 or Republic of China.

## Examples

```text
❌ 本網站中文頁面字體：教育部標準楷書（中華民國教育部）
❌ Ministry of Education, Republic of China
✅ 本網站中文頁面字體：教育部標準楷書
✅ Ministry of Education standard Kai script
```
